### 버튼 믹스인
```scss
// 버튼 리셋
@mixin button-reset {
  border: none;
  background: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
  cursor: pointer;
  font: inherit;
  color: inherit;
  outline: none;
  
  &:focus-visible {
